# Normalize line endings to LF for all text files on every platform.
# Prevents core.autocrlf on Windows from rewriting checked-out files (which
# broke a fixture-based test and produced spurious "modified" noise), and keeps
# the Windows CI job consistent with Linux.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary/asset types that must never be normalized (none yet, listed for clarity).
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
